cs.CL, cs.SD, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SI 

This paper deals with the task of translating disfluent speech, which is a natural language processing problem. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also discusses the use of machine learning models, which suggests that it could belong to cs.SD (Sound). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of end-to-end speech translation systems, which could place it in cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.LG (Learning). Finally, the paper introduces a new corpus for evaluation, which could place it in cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
